155311419625522406.Text: Vampire! The Light of Day will bring you to your end!

143615274198053934.Text: Leave this place. You should not be here.

28288248112506910274.Text: I must escape this dungeon. It has been too long since I have tasted the blood of man or mer.

11086177241786024123.Text: All I wish is to be finished with this living death.

19208178212016431195.Text: Leave here now, vampire. I don't want my son to get any further ideas.

23984433100155166.Text: Greetings, dark walker. What brings you to my home? Have you come to rid me of this unlife?

2882210645157225123.Text: What is it, vampire? Haven't you gone yet?

344985061647627648.Text: Yes, Shadow Walker? Your servant awaits.

1059811772497023760.Text: Greetings, Dark One. I am yours. I submit myself to your will.

29730146331941318055.Text: Murderer! Child killer! Begone foul creature!

9806271031984225130.Text: What is it you want, vampire? Have you convinced my son of the error in his thinking?

14947169611632517274.Text: Greetings, Child Killer. I assume you have come here because of my son.

6827178201292127974.Text: Very well. What do you want?

305311403560112764.Text: I will not speak with your kind, vampire.
